with a stopwatch

00:11:03.653 --> 00:11:06.320 align:middle line:84%
and see, how many nails can they
put in the bottom of that shoe?

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:08.330 align:middle line:84%
And 30 seconds-- well,
get it down to 28.

00:11:08.330 --> 00:11:09.780 align:middle line:90%
Get it down to 20.

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:15.140 align:middle line:84%
So once we start looking
at people as mechanisms

00:11:15.140 --> 00:11:19.640 align:middle line:84%
through which we
extract value, then it

00:11:19.640 --> 00:11:23.090 align:middle line:84%
wasn't too long until
our education system

00:11:23.090 --> 00:11:25.280 align:middle line:90%
kind of flipped on its head.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:29.810 align:middle line:84%
Public education was
originally invented as kind

00:11:29.810 --> 00:11:31.910 align:middle line:90%
of a mercy or a compensation.

00:11:31.910 --> 00:11:34.790 align:middle line:84%
It was so that the coal
miner could come home

00:11:34.790 --> 00:11:38.120 align:middle line:84%
after a day of work and
be able to read a novel

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:40.670 align:middle line:84%
and appreciate it or be
able to read the paper

00:11:40.670 --> 00:11:45.140 align:middle line:84%
and then vote effectively
or intelligently.

00:11:45.140 --> 00:11:48.300 align:middle line:84%
It was compensation
for a life of hard work

00:11:48.300 --> 00:11:52.220 align:middle line:84%
so you could have the dignity
of having a mind that actually

00:11:52.220 --> 00:11:53.180 align:middle line:90%
functioned.

00:11:53.180 --> 00:11:54.950 align:middle line:90%
But slowly, over time--

00:11:54.950 --> 00:11:58.790 align:middle line:84%
and I guess because of time
and the value of efficiency,

00:11:58.790 --> 00:12:04.170 align:middle line:84%
