students to learn?

00:12:18.030 --> 00:12:20.810 align:middle line:84%
What do you want them to
know so they can get jobs?

00:12:20.810 --> 00:12:22.220 align:middle line:84%
How do you want
us to train them?

00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:26.720 align:middle line:84%
So corporations are just
externalizing employee training

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:28.520 align:middle line:90%
