00:12:28.520 --> 00:12:31.030 align:middle line:90%
So what is that?

00:12:31.030 --> 00:12:32.030 align:middle line:90%
I mean, there's a model.

00:12:32.030 --> 00:12:35.600 align:middle line:84%
It's the Prussian model of
education, where the school is

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:38.180 align:middle line:84%
