00:18:01.180 --> 00:18:07.750 align:middle line:84%
it's just a reflection of the
complexity of collaboration

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:08.870 align:middle line:90%
that we were able to do.

00:18:08.870 --> 00:18:10.975 align:middle line:84%
And that's because
