our inevitable extinction,

00:42:47.990 --> 00:42:50.450 align:middle line:84%
and I was like,
no, humans matter,

00:42:50.450 --> 00:42:51.745 align:middle line:90%
we should have a human future.

00:42:51.745 --> 00:42:53.120 align:middle line:84%
