00:43:44.670 --> 00:43:48.890 align:middle line:84%
They just have to
rekindle their humanness.

00:43:48.890 --> 00:43:51.780 align:middle line:84%
So that's all that really
being on team human.

00:43:51.780 --> 00:43:52.580 align:middle line:90%
It's funny.

