as we don't try to
techno-solutionize everything.

00:53:42.880 --> 00:53:45.280 align:middle line:84%
As long as we don't think
that everything in reality

00:53:45.280 --> 00:53:49.180 align:middle line:84%
is a data point that
can be somehow processed

00:53:49.180 --> 00:53:51.100 align:middle line:90%
through silicon.

00:53:51.100 --> 00:53:53.230 align:middle line:90%
It's not.

00:53:53.230 --> 00:53:54.410 align:middle line:90%
It can be part of it.

00:53:54.410 --> 00:53:57.520 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the sort of solutions
I'm looking at mostly

00:53:57.520 --> 00:54:04.030 align:middle line:84%
