00:54:52.560 --> 00:54:55.270 align:middle line:84%
because no one's going
to take care of them.

00:54:55.270 --> 00:54:58.050 align:middle line:84%
So there are sort of
simple ways that we

00:54:58.050 --> 00:55:07.830 align:middle line:84%
can unwind some of this
anxious scarcity-based hoarding

00:55:07.830 --> 00:55:10.790 align:middle line:90%
that we're all doing.

00:55:10.790 --> 00:55:14.300 align:middle line:84%
In theory, that's what I'm
talking about these days

00:55:14.300 --> 00:55:19.730 align:middle line:84%
is giving people some of these
simple steps on understanding

00:55:19.730 --> 00:55:23.630 align:middle line:84%
how to create kind
of bounded economies,

00:55:23.630 --> 00:55:27.020 align:middle line:84%
where instead of trying
to earn $10 once,

00:55:27.020 --> 00:55:30.380 align:middle line:84%
you try to figure out how
do I earn $1 10 times that's

00:55:30.380 --> 00:55:33.380 align:middle line:90%
moving through this community?

00:55:33.380 --> 00:55:35.490 align:middle line:90%
And that's not impossible.

00:55:35.490 --> 00:55:40.390 align:middle line:10%
And those have huge
system-wide effects.

00:55:40.390 --> 00:55:43.160 align:middle line:84%
>> So you believe the future
or the way to solve problems is

00:55:43.160 --> 00:55:45.620 align:middle line:90%
local then, essentially?

00:55:45.620 --> 00:55:48.350 align:middle line:84%
And we've gone
upwards in our scale

00:55:48.350 --> 00:55:52.010 align:middle line:84%
from local, to province,
to nation state.

00:55:52.010 --> 00:55:54.620 align:middle line:84%
And you're saying we need to
almost deconstruct the nation

00:55:54.620 --> 00:55:57.200 align:middle line:84%
state, like this idea that the
astronauts when they went up,

00:55:57.200 --> 00:55:58.100 align:middle line:90%
they were like--

00:55:58.100 --> 00:56:02.007 align:middle line:84%
what was it called, that theory
that Scherbakov talked about?

00:56:02.007 --> 00:56:04.340 align:middle line:84%
When they went up, they were
like, oh, actually, there's

00:56:04.340 --> 00:56:05.923 align:middle line:84%
