nation states, right?

00:56:05.923 --> 00:56:07.070 align:middle line:90%
That's just a facade.

00:56:07.070 --> 00:56:07.880 align:middle line:90%
It's a fake idea.

00:56:07.880 --> 00:56:10.070 align:middle line:84%
So you think deconstructing
these national lines

00:56:10.070 --> 00:56:12.672 align:middle line:84%
and these boundaries
is a way to solve this?

00:56:12.672 --> 00:56:13.880 align:middle line:90%
>> It's what's happening now.

00:56:13.880 --> 00:56:17.180 align:middle line:84%
That's why they're building
walls on border lines.

00:56:17.180 --> 00:56:22.220 align:middle line:10%
It's because the
boundaries have dissolved.

00:56:22.220 --> 00:56:24.470 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we all know this
because we studied history.

00:56:24.470 --> 00:56:27.110 align:middle line:84%
There were city-states,
and the city-states

00:56:27.110 --> 00:56:29.685 align:middle line:84%
gave way to nation states,
which are abstractions.

00:56:29.685 --> 00:56:31.560 align:middle line:84%
It's like, no, you're
not a Venetian anymore.

00:56:31.560 --> 00:56:32.780 align:middle line:90%
Now, you're an Italian.

00:56:32.780 --> 00:56:33.830 align:middle line:90%
It's like, what's that?

00:56:33.830 --> 00:56:34.310 align:middle line:90%
Don't worry.

00:56:34.310 --> 00:56:35.300 align:middle line:90%
It's what you are.

00:56:35.300 --> 00:56:36.770 align:middle line:84%
And these are the
lines around it.

00:56:36.770 --> 00:56:38.750 align:middle line:10%
So it was these
abstractions that were

00:56:38.750 --> 00:56:41.860 align:middle line:10%
created in order to really--

00:56:41.860 --> 00:56:44.930 align:middle line:10%
well, to empower
nobles over people

00:56:44.930 --> 00:56:49.550 align:middle line:10%
and to create larger-scale
colonial economies.

00:56:49.550 --> 00:56:53.150 align:middle line:84%
So I don't think
it's a matter of--

00:56:53.150 --> 00:56:55.130 align:middle line:84%
if you try to dissolve
nation-state boundaries,

00:56:55.130 --> 00:56:56.330 align:middle line:84%
people are going
to come after you.

00:56:56.330 --> 00:56:57.620 align:middle line:90%
They're going to get scared.

00:56:57.620 --> 00:56:59.390 align:middle line:84%
So instead, what
I'm asking people

00:56:59.390 --> 00:57:02.900 align:middle line:84%
to do is kind of just
reify your local reality.

00:57:02.900 --> 00:57:08.580 align:middle line:84%
Have 80% of what you do and care
about come from where you are.

00:57:08.580 --> 00:57:12.800 align:middle line:84%
And then kind of the primacy of
the nation state will go down.

00:57:12.800 --> 00:57:15.380 align:middle line:84%
You know, yes, you can still
have international trade.

00:57:15.380 --> 00:57:16.685 align:middle line:90%
You can still get your iPhone.

00:57:16.685 --> 00:57:18.560 align:middle line:84%
You can still do all
that if you really want.

00:57:18.560 --> 00:57:20.900 align:middle line:84%
But let that be kind
of 20% of the economy

00:57:20.900 --> 00:57:24.240 align:middle line:90%
rather than 90% of it.

00:57:24.240 --> 00:57:27.230 align:middle line:84%
And if we don't do that
consciously, it's going

00:57:27.230 --> 00:57:29.420 align:middle line:90%
to do it for us, you know?

00:57:29.420 --> 00:57:33.290 align:middle line:84%
Between climate change, economic
collapse, and trade wars,

00:57:33.290 --> 00:57:34.900 align:middle line:84%
and God knows what,
you're not going

00:57:34.900 --> 00:57:36.830 align:middle line:84%
to be getting those
things anyway,

00:57:36.830 --> 00:57:42.710 align:middle line:84%
so start to learn how
to live at human scale.

00:57:42.710 --> 00:57:45.380 align:middle line:84%
Because it's not a
terrible limitation.

00:57:45.380 --> 00:57:46.620 align:middle line:90%
This is your body.

00:57:46.620 --> 00:57:49.130 align:middle line:90%
This is your scale.

00:57:49.130 --> 00:57:53.480 align:middle line:84%
So if you live at that
scale, you end up,

00:57:53.480 --> 00:57:56.180 align:middle line:90%
I think, so much happier.

00:57:56.180 --> 00:57:58.940 align:middle line:84%
I mean, yeah, so we're going
to have to look at that

00:57:58.940 --> 00:58:00.740 align:middle line:84%
and say, well what are
people entitled to?

00:58:00.740 --> 00:58:04.010 align:middle line:84%
All right, everyone in the world
