00:58:04.010 --> 00:58:05.610 align:middle line:90%
trips.

00:58:05.610 --> 00:58:08.090 align:middle line:84%
So you get one trip after
high school before college.

00:58:08.090 --> 00:58:09.480 align:middle line:90%
You go, where do you want to go?

00:58:09.480 --> 00:58:10.280 align:middle line:90%
Everyone signs up.

00:58:10.280 --> 00:58:12.650 align:middle line:84%
And then, you get one more
maybe when you retire.

00:58:12.650 --> 00:58:13.932 align:middle line:90%
You get to take another trip.

00:58:13.932 --> 00:58:15.890 align:middle line:84%
But no, we're not going
to get-- everyone's not

00:58:15.890 --> 00:58:18.348 align:middle line:84%
